article_title: Wichita woman found safe; Silver Alert canceled
article_text:
Police have canceled a Silver Alert issued for a woman last seen in west Wichita.

Edith Marks has been located and is safe.

She had last been seen Friday morning near Central and Ridge Road. Marks has dementia and alzheimer's disease. She is not familiar with Wichita and has no friends that she visits.
